dren performed better on language development tests, suggesting that teaching deaf children sign language before cochlear implantation is beneficial to language development (2). Therefore, it can be seen how the misconception that learning sign language could hamper language development hinders speech development (1). Additionally, sign language must be introduced to children as early as possible because there is an optimum age for acquiring languages, including sign language (1). Similar to the decline in one’s ability to learn a new language after a certain age, studies have shown cases where deaf children with later sign language exposure had difficulty learning complex sign language grammatical structures (1).%0a%3c %0a%3c People should be aware that learning sign language does not hinder a child’s spoken language development. And to prevent a delay in language development, families of deaf babies should introduce deaf children to sign language as early as possible (1).%0a%3c 1. https://www.nidcd.nih.gov/health/cochlear-implants%0a%3c 2. https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/journal-of-laryngology-and-otology/article/outcomes-of-cochlear-implantation-in-deaf-children-of-deaf-parents-comparative-study/A949F20D96D996073FBB47590F4F85F2%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Expansions:%0a%3c [[#expansions]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#expansionsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%3c %0a%3c (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:elseif [ equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:andrewid} '' || equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:section} '' ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c You must enter your andrew ID and section before submitting an expansion. %0a%3c %0a%3c (:else:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Comments%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:if equal {$Author} {$:Author}:)%0a%3c !!Ch